    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "No I believe it is an issue related to instantsearch using Promises which IE11 does not support.  polyfill.io would be one way of fixing the issue.  I'm sorry I haven't done a lot of digging into this.  I only know that if I try to use the 'searchFunction' to do a multi index search it generates the 'Promise' error in IE11 but it doesn't do it in Chrome.  IE11 is fine as long as I don't use the 'searchFunction'.  However as soon as I try to use / define a 'searchFunction' IE11 starts producing the error and the search no longer functions as expected.",
